text: Bärbel Bas (; born 3 May 1968) is a German politician. She is a member of the Social Democratic Party (SPD). She was the 14th president of the Bundestag from 2021 to 2025. She has been a member of the German Bundestag since the federal election in 2009. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the German Bundestag Category:Politicians of the Social Democratic Party of Germany Category:Politicians from North Rhine- Westphalia Category:People from Duisburg
